cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image translation, specifically translating face images from one domain to another. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also uses GANs for training, which is a popular technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with multimedia (cs.MM) as it focuses on image translation. Finally, the paper uses a novel weight sharing technique for GANs, which could fall under the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
